<h2>How to Optimize AI Images for SEO</h2>
<p>Generating the image is step one. Optimizing it for search engines and page speed is where most teams fail.</p>
<h3>File Naming</h3>
<p>Search engines read file names. A descriptive name tells Google what the image contains before it even processes the visual.</p>
